Step 1: Run Locally
myBank/
├── cmd/
│   └── myBank/
│       └── main.go
├── internal/
│   ├── account/
│   │   ├── account.go
│   │   ├── account_service.go
│   │   └── transfer_service.go
├── db/
│   ├── init.go
│   └── schema.sql
├── go.mod
└── go.sum

go run ./cmd/myBank/main.go -action=create -owner="Alice"

Step 2: Build the Project
Build the Project: go build -o myBank ./cmd/myBank/
Run the Built Binary: ./myBank -action=create -owner="Alice"

Step 3: Test

Using go-sqlmock package to mock database

gin for api